cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MA, cs.SY, cs.CL 

The paper deals with multi-agent scenarios and proposes a model for efficient training with back-propagation. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The paper also deals with communication and control mechanisms, which suggests that it may belong to the Multi-Agent Systems (cs.MA) and Systems and Control (cs.SY) sub-categories. Finally, the paper uses tasks from the StarCraft BroodWars game, which suggests that it may belong to the Computational Linguistics (cs.CL) sub-category, as this game involves natural language interactions between players.
